Connection refused: Cause:  openssh-client not working properly.  Remedy:  Wait for few seconds after VM is created.
Permissiondenied:  Cause:  User hos no permissions to use private key. Remedy: Check the user type and change permissions of private key.
Host key verification failed: Unable to verify Host key. Remedy:  echo 'host_key_checking = False' | sudo tee -a /etc/ansible/ansible.cfg
